        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6097",
        "content": "She sees a sea of faces like a dream; She sees herself a queen of song once more; She sees lips part in rapture, eyes agleam; She sings as never once she sang before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
