        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6097",
        "content": "A lame tramp comes along the railway track, A grizzled dog whose day is nearly done: He passes, pauses, then comes slowly back And listens there-an audience of one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
