        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6097",
        "content": "Well, thankee kindly, sir, I don't mind if I do.\") A drivelling, dirty gin joint fiend, the butt of the bar room joke; Sunk and sodden and hopeless-\"Another?",
